{"tid":356339,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"俄逐美外交官　特感激普京：可省錢","createTime":"2017-08-12T04:05:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-13T10:56:27.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c7e7bc34b468e95b25f9cb695d0a8f35bf063cb1","tid":356339,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T04:05:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20118904&amp;category_guid=15335&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170812\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20118904%26category_guid%3D15335%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170812&d=OqD2C0xP3Ur7qn00Z6%2FwtaNGKT0mDZcTD8WJHRevFdc%3D&h=92a92fc2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20118904%26category_guid%3D15335%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170812&h=45294d14\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20118904&amp;category_guid=15335&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170812</a><br />\n<br />\n俄逐美外交官　特感激普京：可省錢<br />\n<br />\n國際新聞&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n莫斯科美國駐俄大使館<br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯總統普京早前下令驅逐數百名美國外交人員，身陷通俄門風波的美國總統特朗普前日卻不避嫌，回應指這能為美國節省很多開支，對普京的協助「非常感激」。<br />\n<br />\n國務院官員震驚<br />\n<br />\n正在休假的特朗普前日聽取國家安全簡報後，與記者談到普京下令9月1日前驅逐755名美國人員時表示：「我希望感謝普京，因為我們正計劃裁減開支&hellip;&hellip;他們（美國人員）確實沒有理由要回去，因此我非常感激俄方能縮減美國開支。我們節省了很多金錢。」白宮尚未回應事件。<br />\n未知特朗普是否只是開玩笑，惟消息指國務院官員對此大為震驚。國務卿本周初指會於9月1日對俄方行動採取正式回應。曾負責政務的前副國務卿伯恩斯形容特朗普的言論「怪異」，「若他是開玩笑，他應知道不應這樣做；若他不是，這是前所未見，一名總統竟不為被驅外交人員辯護」。<br />\n美聯社/路透社"},{"pid":"c5cdb03371a169401c2f19a3764f8e86b024366a","tid":356339,"uid":99364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T04:11:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"77fd0281e7bdb6df83e9c65c74c12ca25d4e483e","tid":356339,"uid":23170,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T04:11:52.000Z","msg":"我想問要為班外交官辯護啲乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8ab07ba5d6b07f0f6e703ab16b77a33ec80cff5","tid":356339,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T04:12:59.000Z","msg":"真係癡線既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8087c64d01321da7027a6a177cd06fedc60cf7f","tid":356339,"uid":26156,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T04:14:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d2a041c333e8b3cd30713247f9a7a31fb81004f5","tid":356339,"uid":73241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T04:16:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33902ecb6b19d4caa4eae5fb2ba434b12b5e995f","tid":356339,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T10:56:27.000Z","msg":"印度兵佔領中國領土,  習總感激:「可省錢, 唔洗用咁多錢 去管治該地」"}]}